Afghanistan’s Karzai Plans Third Term After 2014, Bild Says

-- B y   R a i n e r   B u e r g i n
-- 
2011-12-05T07:16:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-05/afghanistan-s-karzai-plans-third-term-after-2014-bild-says.html
Afghan President Hamid Karzai plans
to change the country’s constitution and run for a third term in
office after 2014,  Germany ’s  Bild-Zeitung  reported, citing a
classified report by Germany’s BND intelligence agency from
September.  To contact the reporter on this story:
